                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">on the Second Count.</hi>
                  </rs> 
                  <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted at this Court, in April</hi>, 1863, <hi rend="italic">when he was sentenced to three</hi>
               </p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186607090038"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">years penal servitude—to this he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18660709-619-punishment-28" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18660709-619-punishment-28" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
